<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f7f7f7; padding: 20px;">
    <div
        style="background: white; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px #ccc;">
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <img src="<%= S3_URL %>/logo.png" alt="MomSays Logo" style="width: 120px;" />
        </div>
        <h2 style="text-align: center; color: #f44336;">Hi <%= name %>,</h2>
        <p>We received a request to reset your MomSays password. You can reset your password by clicking the button
            below:</p>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="<%= resetLink %>"
                style="background-color: #4caf50; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px;">Reset
                Password</a>
        </div>

        <p>If you didn’t request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <p style="color: gray; font-size: 12px;">This link will expire in 1 hour for security reasons.</p>
        <p>Thank you,<br />The MomSays Team</p>
        <br />
        <p style="color: gray; font-size: 12px;">© 2025 MomSays. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>